      "Code": "Dic;\nesc;\ndes;\ncat;\nmod;\nqes;\nPin = Dic[\"Pin\"];\nL   = Dic[\"L\"  ];\nH   = Dic[\"H\"  ];\ne   = Dic[\"e\"  ];\nm   = L * -des;\n//------------------------------------\nPsu = Geometry.Scale ( Pin  , esc  );\nPs2 = Psu.Translate  ( m , 0 , H   );\nPo2 = Ps2.Offset     ( -e          );\nsol = Solid.ByLoft   ( [Pin , Ps2] );\n//------------------------------------\nMastro ( mod , sol , cat );\nEstais ( Pin , Ps2 , qes );"
