      "Code": "l;\nh;\ne;\npt;\nf  =  0.050;\na  =  0.500;\nm  =  0.500;\ni  = [1,2,7,11,15,18,17,12,8,4];\n//------------------------------------\ny  = l * [ -m,     -f,   0    ,f   , m ];\nz  = h * [  0, -0.1*a, -0.8*a , -2*a   ];\n//------------------------------------\nLP  = Point.ByCoordinates (0, y<1>, z);\nLF  = List.Flatten ( LP , 1 );\nLV  = LF[i];\nTB  = PolyCurve.ByPoints(LV, 1);\nTI  = TB.Offset(-e);\nET  = Line.ByStartPointEndPoint(LV[3], LV[8]);\nTA  = Geometry.Translate(TB, Point.AsVector(pt[3]));"
